    "body": "aoti_torch_call_dispatcher is meant to call different ops, so the op must not be static. Otherwise, every call to this API will call the first op that was ever called, which is not the intended behavior of any human being.\r\n\r\nStack from [ghstack](https://github.com/ezyang/ghstack) (oldest at bottom):\n* #149230\n* #149052\n* __->__ #149208\n\r\n",
